<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Koordinaten Filter Box</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: #1a1f2e; color: #e8eaf0;
    min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  header {
    background: #12161f; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3148;
    padding: 12px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  header .logo {
    width: 38px; height: 38px; background: #e8542a; border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0; padding: 3px;
  }
  header .logo svg .c-pin         { fill: white; }
  header .logo svg .c-hole        { fill: #e8542a; }
  header .logo svg .c-stroke      { stroke: white; stroke-width: 2.5; stroke-linecap: round; }
  header .logo svg .c-stroke-thick{ stroke: white; stroke-width: 3; stroke-linecap: round; }
  header h1 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #e8eaf0; }
  header span { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7494; margin-left: 4px; }
  .header-right {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-left: auto;
  }
  .header-right a {
    font-size: 11px; color: #6b7494; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .header-right a:hover { color: #e8eaf0; }
  .warning-text {
    font-size: 11px; color: #e8542a; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .layout {
    display: flex; flex: 1; min-height: 0; height: calc(100vh - 55px);
  }
  .map-column {
    flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-width: 0; position: relative;
  }
  .radius-bar {
    background: #12161f; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3148;
    padding: 9px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center;
    gap: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .radius-bar .r-label {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #6b7494; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .radius-presets { display: flex; gap: 5px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .preset-btn {
    padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 12px; border: 1px solid #2a3148;
    border-radius: 20px; background: #1a1f2e; color: #9ba3c0;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; font-family: inherit; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .preset-btn:hover { border-color: #e8542a; color: #e8eaf0; }
  .preset-btn.active { background: #e8542a; border-color: #e8542a; color: white; font-weight: 600; }
  .slider-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex: 1; min-width: 120px; }
  .slider-wrap .sl-end { font-size: 10px; color: #4a5270; white-space: nowrap; }
  input[type="range"] {
    flex: 1; -webkit-appearance: none; height: 4px;
    background: #2a3148; border-radius: 2px; outline: none; cursor: pointer;
  }
  input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb {
    -webkit-appearance: none; width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #e8542a; cursor: pointer; border: 2px solid #12161f;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #e8542a;
  }
  input[type="range"]::-moz-range-thumb {
    width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #e8542a; cursor: pointer; border: 2px solid #12161f;
  }
  .radius-value-display {
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #e8542a;
    min-width: 68px; text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .autozoom-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 4px 11px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; border: 1px solid #2a3148; border-radius: 20px;
    background: #1a1f2e; color: #9ba3c0; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s; font-family: inherit; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .autozoom-btn .az-dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #3a4060; transition: background 0.2s; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .autozoom-btn.on { border-color: #5db83a; color: #97c459; }
  .autozoom-btn.on .az-dot { background: #5db83a; }
  .autozoom-btn:hover { border-color: #e8542a; color: #e8eaf0; }
  .km-toggle-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 4px 11px;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; border: 1px solid #2a3148; border-radius: 20px;
    background: #1a1f2e; color: #9ba3c0; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s; font-family: inherit; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .km-toggle-btn .az-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #3a4060; transition: background 0.2s; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .km-toggle-btn.on { border-color: #1a6fbb; color: #6aaee8; }
  .km-toggle-btn.on .az-dot { background: #1a6fbb; }
  .km-toggle-btn:hover { border-color: #e8542a; color: #e8eaf0; }
  #map { flex: 1; background: #0d1117; cursor: crosshair; }
  .map-hint-overlay {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    background: rgba(18,22,31,0.88); border: 1px solid #2a3148;
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 13px; color: #9ba3c0;
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 1000; white-space: nowrap; transition: opacity 0.4s;
  }
  .map-hint-overlay.hidden { opacity: 0; }
  .coord-status {
    background: #12161f; border-top: 1px solid #2a3148;
    padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7494;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .coord-status .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #3a4060; flex-shrink: 0; transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .coord-status .dot.active { background: #5db83a; }
  .coord-status .coords-text { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; color: #9ba3c0; }
  .manual-input-bar {
    background: #12161f; border-top: 1px solid #2a3148;
    padding: 9px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .manual-input-bar .m-label {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #4a5270; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .manual-input-bar input[type="text"] {
    flex: 1; background: #1a1f2e; border: 1px solid #2a3148;
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 13px;
    color: #e8eaf0; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.15s; font-family: inherit;
  }
  .manual-input-bar input[type="text"]:focus { border-color: #e8542a; }
  .manual-input-bar input::placeholder { color: #3a4060; }
  .btn-parse {
    background: #e8542a; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s; font-family: inherit; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .btn-parse:hover { background: #d4481e; }
  .sidebar {
    width: 390px; flex-shrink: 0; background: #12161f;
    border-left: 1px solid #2a3148; display: flex;
    flex-direction: column; overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .section { padding: 16px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2436; }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #6b7494; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .status-dot {
    display: inline-block; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #3a4060; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle; transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .status-dot.active { background: #5db83a; }
  .diba-panel { background: #f5f6f9; border: 2px solid #c8cdd8; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; }
  .diba-panel-header {
    background: #e8eaf0; border-bottom: 2px solid #c8cdd8;
    padding: 8px 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px;
  }
  .funnel-icon-wrap {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 26px; height: 26px; background: #0e4d8f;
    border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .diba-badge {
    background: #1a6fbb; color: white; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 3px; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .diba-title-text { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a2a40; }
  .filter-rows { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .filter-group-sep {
    background: #dde0e8; padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #7a8599;
    border-top: 1px solid #c8cdd8;
  }
  .filter-group-sep:first-child { border-top: none; }
  .filter-row {
    display: flex; align-items: stretch; background: #fff;
    border-top: 1px solid #dde0e8; height: 38px;
  }
  .filter-row .field-name {
    width: 92px; flex-shrink: 0; padding: 0 10px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
    color: #333; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    border-right: 1px solid #dde0e8; background: #f0f2f6;
    display: flex; align-items: center; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .filter-row .operator {
    width: 106px; flex-shrink: 0; padding: 0 8px; font-size: 11px; color: #555;
    border-right: 1px solid #dde0e8; background: #f8f9fb;
    display: flex; align-items: center; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .filter-row .coord-value {
    flex: 1; min-width: 0; padding: 0 10px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;
    font-family: 'Consolas', 'Menlo', 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; background: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .filter-row .coord-value.empty { color: #bbb; font-weight: 400; font-size: 11px; font-family: inherit; }
  .filter-row .btn-copy {
    flex-shrink: 0; background: #eef2f8; border: none; border-left: 1px solid #dde0e8;
    padding: 0 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #1a6fbb; cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s; white-space: nowrap; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .filter-row .btn-copy:hover { background: #dce6f5; color: #0d4e8a; }
  .filter-row .btn-copy.copied { background: #eaf5e8; color: #2f7a18; }
  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .layout { flex-direction: column; height: auto; }
    .sidebar { width: 100%; border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid #2a3148; }
    #map { height: 340px; }
  }
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); z-index: 9000;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .modal-box {
    background: #1a1f2e; border: 1px solid #2a3148; border-radius: 10px;
    max-width: 680px; width: 100%; max-height: 85vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .modal-header {
    background: #12161f; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3148;
    padding: 16px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .modal-header h2 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #e8eaf0; }
  .modal-close {
    background: none; border: none; color: #6b7494;
    font-size: 22px; cursor: pointer; line-height: 1; padding: 0 4px; transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .modal-close:hover { color: #e8eaf0; }
  .modal-body {
    overflow-y: auto; padding: 24px; color: #c8cfe0; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .modal-body h3 {
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #e8542a;
    margin: 22px 0 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3148; padding-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .modal-body h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .modal-body p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .modal-body ul { margin: 0 0 10px 20px; }
  .modal-body li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .modal-body a { color: #7fc0f5; text-decoration: none; }
  .modal-body a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .modal-body .highlight {
    background: #12161f; border: 1px solid #2a3148;
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo" id="logo-btn" title="Koordinaten Filter Box">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" width="32" height="32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle class="c-pin" cx="20" cy="8" r="6"/>
      <circle class="c-hole" cx="20" cy="8" r="2.8"/>
      <path class="c-pin" d="M17.8 13.5 L22.2 13.5 L20 21 Z"/>
      <line class="c-stroke" x1="3" y1="26" x2="37" y2="26"/>
      <line class="c-stroke" x1="3" y1="36" x2="37" y2="36"/>
      <line class="c-stroke-thick" x1="8"  y1="23" x2="8"  y2="39"/>
      <line class="c-stroke-thick" x1="16" y1="23" x2="16" y2="39"/>
      <line class="c-stroke-thick" x1="24" y1="23" x2="24" y2="39"/>
      <line class="c-stroke-thick" x1="32" y1="23" x2="32" y2="39"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <h1>Koordinaten Filter Box <span>— Bounding Box Rechner</span></h1>
  <div class="header-right">
    <span class="warning-text">⚠ Internes Werkzeug · Experimentell · Nur für autorisierten Zugang</span>
    <a href="#" onclick="openDatenschutz(); return false;">Datenschutzerklärung</a>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="layout">

  <!-- MAP COLUMN -->
  <div class="map-column">
    <div class="radius-bar">
      <div class="r-label">Radius</div>
      <div class="radius-presets">
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(10)">10 m</button>
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(50)">50 m</button>
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(100)">100 m</button>
        <button class="preset-btn active" onclick="setRadius(250)">250 m</button>
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(500)">500 m</button>
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(1000)">1 km</button>
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(2500)">2,5 km</button>
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(5000)">5 km</button>
        <button class="preset-btn"        onclick="setRadius(10000)">10 km</button>
      </div>
      <div class="slider-wrap">
        <span class="sl-end">10 m</span>
        <input type="range" id="radius-slider" min="0" max="100" value="43" oninput="onSliderChange(this.value)"/>
        <span class="sl-end">10 km</span>
      </div>
      <div class="radius-value-display" id="radius-display">250 m</div>
      <button class="autozoom-btn on" id="autozoom-btn" onclick="toggleAutoZoom()">
        <span class="az-dot"></span>Auto-Zoom
      </button>
      <button class="km-toggle-btn on" id="km-toggle-btn" onclick="toggleKmLabels()">
        <span class="az-dot"></span>km-Labels
      </button>
    </div>

    <div id="map"></div>
    <div class="map-hint-overlay" id="map-hint">Auf Karte klicken — Punkt setzen</div>

    <div class="coord-status">
      <div class="dot" id="status-dot-map"></div>
      <span class="coords-text" id="coords-display">Noch kein Punkt gesetzt</span>
    </div>

    <div class="manual-input-bar">
      <div class="m-label">Manuell</div>
      <input type="text" id="gmaps-input" placeholder="Lat, Long  —  z.B. 49.01244, 12.03273 (aus Google Maps)" />
      <button class="btn-parse" onclick="parseGMaps()">Setzen</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SIDEBAR -->
  <div class="sidebar">
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">Zu km / Betriebsstelle springen</div>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:6px; align-items:center;">
        <input type="text" id="jump-input" placeholder="45,45 oder Regensburg"
          style="flex:1; background:#1a1f2e; border:1px solid #2a3148; border-radius:6px;
                 padding:7px 10px; font-size:12px; color:#e8eaf0; outline:none; font-family:inherit;"
          oninput="showJumpSuggestions(this.value)"
          onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter') jumpToFirst()"/>
        <button onclick="jumpToFirst()"
          style="background:#e8542a; color:white; border:none; border-radius:6px;
                 padding:7px 12px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit;">
          ↵
        </button>
      </div>
      <div id="jump-suggestions" style="margin-top:6px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:3px;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section" style="flex:1;">
      <div class="section-title">
        <span class="status-dot" id="status-dot"></span>Koordinaten für DiBa
      </div>
      <div class="diba-panel">
        <div class="diba-panel-header">
          <span class="diba-badge">DiBa</span>
          <span class="diba-title-text">Koordinaten für Geo-Daten Filter</span>
          <div class="funnel-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M1.5 2.5 L14.5 2.5 L9.5 8.0 L9.5 13.0 L8.5 13.8 L6.5 13.0 L6.5 8.0 Z" fill="white"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="filter-rows">
          <div class="filter-group-sep">Latitude</div>
          <div class="filter-row">
            <div class="field-name">LATITUDE</div>
            <div class="operator">größer gleich</div>
            <div class="coord-value empty" id="val-lat-min">—</div>
            <button class="btn-copy" onclick="copyVal('val-lat-min', this)">Kopieren</button>
          </div>
          <div class="filter-row">
            <div class="field-name">LATITUDE</div>
            <div class="operator">kleiner gleich</div>
            <div class="coord-value empty" id="val-lat-max">—</div>
            <button class="btn-copy" onclick="copyVal('val-lat-max', this)">Kopieren</button>
          </div>
          <div class="filter-group-sep">Longitude</div>
          <div class="filter-row">
            <div class="field-name">LONGITUDE</div>
            <div class="operator">größer gleich</div>
            <div class="coord-value empty" id="val-long-min">—</div>
            <button class="btn-copy" onclick="copyVal('val-long-min', this)">Kopieren</button>
          </div>
          <div class="filter-row">
            <div class="field-name">LONGITUDE</div>
            <div class="operator">kleiner gleich</div>
            <div class="coord-value empty" id="val-long-max">—</div>
            <button class="btn-copy" onclick="copyVal('val-long-max', this)">Kopieren</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Datenschutz Modal -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="datenschutz-modal" onclick="closeDatenschutzOnOverlay(event)">
  <div class="modal-box">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <h2>Datenschutzerklärung</h2>
      <button class="modal-close" onclick="closeDatenschutz()" title="Schließen">×</button>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="highlight">
        <strong>Kurzfassung:</strong> Diese Anwendung verarbeitet ausschließlich Koordinaten, die Sie selbst eingeben oder auf der Karte auswählen. Es werden keine Daten gespeichert oder an Dritte weitergegeben.
      </div>
      <h3>1. Verantwortliche Stelle</h3>
      <p>Diese Webanwendung wird intern betrieben und richtet sich ausschließlich an autorisierte Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeiter.</p>
      <h3>2. Zweck der Anwendung</h3>
      <p>Die <em>Koordinaten Filter Box</em> ist ein internes Hilfswerkzeug zur Berechnung geografischer Bounding Boxes für den Geo-Daten Filter im System DiBa.</p>
      <h3>3. Verarbeitung personenbezogener Daten</h3>
      <p>Diese Anwendung verarbeitet <strong>keine personenbezogenen Daten</strong>. Es werden keine Cookies gesetzt und kein Tracking durchgeführt. Alle Berechnungen finden ausschließlich lokal in Ihrem Browser statt.</p>
      <h3>4. Kartendaten (externe Dienste)</h3>
      <p>Für die Kartenanzeige werden Kartenkacheln von OpenStreetMap / CARTO geladen (<code>basemaps.cartocdn.com</code>). Dabei wird Ihre IP-Adresse technisch notwendigerweise übertragen. Datenschutzhinweise: <a href="https://carto.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">carto.com/privacy</a></p>
      <h3>5. Kartenbibliothek (Leaflet)</h3>
      <p>Leaflet wird über <code>unpkg.com</code> geladen. Beim ersten Laden kann Ihre IP-Adresse übermittelt werden. Leaflet speichert keine Nutzerdaten.</p>
      <h3>6. Ihre Rechte</h3>
      <p>Bei Fragen zum Datenschutz wenden Sie sich bitte an den betrieblichen Datenschutzbeauftragten.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
const DEG2RAD = Math.PI / 180;
let marker = null, boundingBox = null;
let currentLat = null, currentLng = null;
let currentRadius = 250;
let autoZoom = true;
let kmHighlightMarker = null;

// ── Map ──
const map = L.map('map', { zoomControl: true }).setView([49.1970791, 11.3597205], 10);
L.tileLayer('https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/rastertiles/voyager/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png', {
  attribution: '© OpenStreetMap contributors © CARTO', maxZoom: 19
}).addTo(map);
map.on('click', e => setLocation(e.latlng.lat, e.latlng.lng));

// ── Betriebsstellen-Punkte ──
// Strecke 5850 – 659 Punkte (100m gefiltert)
